cu.explanation_en: Setting the tracking_area_code to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause tracking area configuration failure and prevent proper cell identification.

du.explanation_en: Setting the tracking_area_code to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause tracking area configuration failure and prevent proper cell identification.
du.explanation_zh: 將 tracking_area_code 設定為無效值 'invalid'，會導致追蹤區域配置失敗，並阻止正確的細胞識別。
